      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Module 16的时序图，主题是备份告警和监控。核心流程是临床工程师通过Azure Backup Vault来管理Workload VM的备份。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Clinical Engineer",
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个参与者：ClinEng、Azure、Workload。我想确认一下，Workload VM是备份的目标，对吧？还有，Azure Backup Vault是中间协调者？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Azure Backup Vault是中心节点。流程开始是临床工程师配置备份策略，然后Azure向Workload VM触发快照任务，VM把恢复点发回Azure，最后工程师验证恢复点和报告。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Configure policy",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job",
        "Send recovery point",
        "Validate recovery point & reports"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出三个参与者和标题。标题定为\"Module 16 – Backup Alerts and Monitoring (Sequence)\"，参与者用ClinEng、Azure、Workload的别名显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "participant ClinEng",
        "participant Azure",
        "participant Workload"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第一步行画好了：ClinEng指向Azure的\"Configure policy\"。接下来Azure到Workload的触发消息，我用虚线还是实线？快照触发是异步的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClinEng-Azure: Configure policy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "触发备份任务和返回恢复点都是系统内部响应，用虚线箭头表示异步回调更合适。触发是Azure向Workload发指令，恢复点是Workload回传数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure--Workload",
        "Workload--Azure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，Azure到Workload用虚线标注\"Trigger snapshot/backup job\"，Workload返回虚线\"Send recovery point\"。最后一步验证是ClinEng直接查Azure的数据吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure--Workload: Trigger snapshot/backup job",
        "Workload--Azure: Send recovery point"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，最后一步是ClinEng到Azure的\"Validate recovery point & reports\"，工程师在Portal里检查恢复点有效性和监控报告。这样整个监控闭环就完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClinEng-Azure: Validate recovery point & reports"
